title: Man, 29, shot to death on porch in Northeast Baltimore
text:
Published By: Baltimore Sun: Breaking - Today 
A 29-year-old man was shot to death Thursday on a porch in Northeast Baltimore, police said, just blocks from a shooting earlier in the week...
